epo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Package and Build Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/coq-community/docker-coq\">Docker-Coq</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/coq-community/docker-coq\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":25,\"repo\":\"coq-community/docker-coq\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Docker images for many versions of Coq.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.labri.fr/perso/casteran/CoqArt/\">Coq'Art</a> - The first book dedicated to Coq.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://softwarefoundations.cis.upenn.edu\">Software Foundations</a> - Series of Coq-based textbooks on logic, functional programming, and foundations of programming languages, aimed at being accessible to beginners.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://adam.chlipala.net/cpdt/\">Certified Programming with Dependent Types</a> - Textbook about practical engineering with Coq which teaches advanced practical tricks and a very specific style of proof.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://adam.chlipala.net/frap/\">Formal Reasoning About Programs</a> - Book that simultaneously provides a general introduction to formal logical reasoning about the correctness of programs and to using Coq for this purpose.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ilyasergey.net/pnp/\">Programs and Proofs</a> - Book that gives a brief and practically-oriented introduction to interactive proofs in Coq which emphasizes the computational nature of inductive reasoning about decidable propositions via a small set of primitives from the SSReflect proof language.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Books</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://iste.co.uk/book.php?id=1238\">Computer Arithmetic and Formal Proofs</a> - Book that describes how to formally specify and verify floating-point algorithms in Coq using the Flocq library.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T02:24:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Frameworks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/CoqEAL/CoqEAL\">CoqEAL</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/CoqEAL/CoqEAL\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">49</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":49,\"repo\":\"CoqEAL/CoqEAL\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Framework to ease change of data representations in proofs.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T01:14:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Frameworks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://querycert.github.io\">Q*cert</a> - Platform for implementing and verifying query compilers.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T01:14:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Libraries</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/plclub/metalib\">Metalib</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/plclub/metalib\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">49</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":49,\"repo\":\"plclub/metalib\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Library for programming language metatheory using locally nameless variable binding representations.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T01:14:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"coq-community/awesome-coq","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Tools</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools\">coq-tools</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,san